groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: WO-9.1 - Eagleview Oasis - Multi
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: A short, simple two stage multi-cache to bring you to the oasis.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
This area was just begging to have a cache (or caches) placed here. A prototypical wild oasis. A forest, meadows and ponds wedged between highways, roads, and commercial and retail buildings.
Stage 1 is a micro containing just the coordinates for stage 2. Stage 2 is a large small or a small regular depending on how you look at it.
I hope you enjoy your time here.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: [Stage 1:] Film canister in rocks [Stage 2: Should be obvious, I'll add a hint if people can't find it.]

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: A walk in the woods after dinner at Ron's. Found with dawnie22 and 19acassel. TFTC
